    "body": "```\nthread 'main' (232149) panicked at src/bin/cargo-kmiri-helper.rs:158:18:\ncalled `Result::unwrap()` on an `Err` value: Error(\"trailing characters\", line: 7388, column: 2)\n```\n\n```\n  {\n    \"instance\": \"<&'a [syn::attr::Attribute] as syn::attr::FilterAttrs<'a>>::inner\",\n    \"source_file\": \"/home/zjp/.cargo/registry/src/index.crates.io-1949cf8c6b5b557f/syn-1.0.109/src/attr.rs\",\n    \"line_start\": 486,\n    \"line_end\": 494\n  }\n]056 👈,\n    \"line_end\": 1056\n  },\n  {\n    \"instance\": \"<proc_macro2::Ident as core::cmp::Ord>::cmp\",\n    \"source_file\": \"/home/zjp/.cargo/registry/src/index.crates.io-1949cf8c6b5b557f/proc-macro2-1.0.106/src/lib.rs\",\n    \"line_start\": 1070,\n    \"line_end\": 1070\n  },\n```\n\nThis probably results from concurrent writes to the same file?\n\n```\n 602 │ [[package]]\n 603 │ name = \"syn\"\n 604 │ version = \"1.0.109\"\n 605 │ source = \"registry+https://github.com/rust-lang/crates.io-index\"\n 606 │ checksum = \"72b64191b275b66ffe2469e8af2c1cfe3bafa67b529ead792a6d0160888b4237\"\n 607 │ dependencies = [\n 608 │  \"proc-macro2\",\n 609 │  \"quote\",\n 610 │  \"unicode-ident\",\n 611 │ ]\n 612 │\n 613 │ [[package]]\n 614 │ name = \"syn\"\n 615 │ version = \"2.0.118\"\n 616 │ source = \"registry+https://github.com/rust-lang/crates.io-index\"\n 617 │ checksum = \"1b9ae57f904213ebb649ce6895b8a66c66f0203b9319718f69a5612a065b1422\"\n 618 │ dependencies = [\n 619 │  \"proc-macro2\",\n 620 │  \"quote\",\n 621 │  \"unicode-ident\",\n 622 │ ]\n```",
